  <brief_title>Study on High-sensitivity Troponin 0h/1h for Rapid Diagnosis of Non-ST-segment Elevation Myocardial Infarction in the Chinese Population</brief_title>
  <official_title>Study the High-sensitivity Troponin 0h/1h for Rapid Diagnosis of Non-ST-segment Elevation Myocardial Infarction in the Chinese Population</official_title>
