  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the study is to establish a high-sensitivity troponin 0h/1h process for the
      diagnosis of patients suspected of NSTEMI for the Chinese population, obtain the inclusion
      and exclusion criteria for diagnosis of these patients and compare the new process with the
      existing diagnosing methods and processes, including the 3h and 6h processes more extensively
      used at present and the ECG combined with troponin diagnosis, so as to explore a confirmation
      model suitable for the Chinese population.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
